sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.adapters

Class PartAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.AbstractRegistrable
      • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.Adapter
        • sk.stuba.fiit.perconik.core.adapters.PartAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.ui.IPartListener2, Listener, PartListener, Registrable

    public class PartAdapter
extends Adapter
implements PartListener
    An abstract adapter class for a PartListener. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating listener objects.

    Extend this class to create a PartListener and override the methods for the events of interest.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pavol Zbell
    See Also:
    Adapter, PartListener
